description: This header file declares internal function prototypes for a Web Server FSM (Finite State Machine) component, including functions for handling HTTP methods and file mapping.

methods.name: WebRooFsmDoGet
methods.description: Handles HTTP GET requests within the FSM.

methods.name: WebRooFsmDoHead
methods.description: Handles HTTP HEAD requests within the FSM.

methods.name: WebRooFsmDoPost
methods.description: Handles HTTP POST requests within the FSM.

methods.name: WebRooFsmMapDiskFile
methods.description: Maps a disk file for serving in the web server context.

methods.name: WebRooFsmGetMimeType
methods.description: Retrieves the MIME type and sub-type for a given file.
